import React from 'react'; function Card({ data }) { return (
DEPART
{data?.depart.toUpperCase()}
ARRIVE
{data?.arrive.toUpperCase()}
DATE
{data.departureDate} - {data?.returnDate}
STOPS
{data?.stops}
AIRLINES
{data?.airlines.toUpperCase()}
PRICE
{data?.price}
); } export default Card;
